{"arkId":"cl010114654","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114654","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Terrine sa doublure et son plateau","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Terrine sa doublure et son plateau"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1754 - 1755","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 605 - Stavros S. Niarchos, Vitrine 14","room":"Salle 605, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1754,"endYear":1755,"imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Germain, Fran\u00e7ois-Thomas","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1726","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1791","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3083671"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"V 4721","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"terrine ; plateau ; orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La terrine, au corps ovale l\u00e9g\u00e8rement renfl\u00e9 est port\u00e9e par quatre pieds \u00e0 triple enroulement avec feuillages de ch\u00eane et glands sur fond amati ;  deux anses \u00e0 enroulements. La ceinture est soulign\u00e9e d\u2019une frise amatie d\u2019enroulements et de filets enrubann\u00e9s. Une doublure amovible pourvue de deux prises. Le couvercle en courbure est orn\u00e9 de cannelures rayonnantes avec une prise compos\u00e9e de deux grenades ouvertes  avec leurs feuilles. Le plateau ovale \u00e0 contours, bord\u00e9 de joncs enrubann\u00e9s, est l\u00e9g\u00e8rement sur\u00e9lev\u00e9 dans sa partie centrale, il est port\u00e9 par quatre pieds en forme de pattes de lion ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s par l\u0027orf\u00e8vre Jean-Charles Roquillet-Desnoyers en 1781-1782 (poin\u00e7ons de ma\u00eetre, jurande, d\u00e9charge).","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; signatures \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9rieur du corps et sous le plateau, \u00ab F. T. GERMAIN ; SCULPR ORFRE DU ROY. FECIT AUX. GALLERIS [sic]. DU. LOUVRE. A PARIS. 1755 \u00bb ; au revers du couvercle, poids grav\u00e9, \u00ab 38 m[arcs] 6 o[nces] 2 g[ros] \u00bb ; \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9rieur de la terrine, marque : \u00ab II \u00bb\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; (terrine, doublure et plateau) ma\u00eetre, fleur de lys couronn\u00e9e, deux grains, lettres FTG et une toison ; jurande, lettre O couronn\u00e9e pour juillet 1754-juillet 1755 ; charge, un A couronn\u00e9 avec une palme et un laurier, pour 1750-1756","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"27,5","displayDimension":"27,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"46","displayDimension":"46 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"25,5","displayDimension":"25,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":7,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5","displayDimension":"5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":9,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"56,5","displayDimension":"56,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":10,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"42","displayDimension":"42 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":11,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","place